{"tid":283813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方日報：倘運海洛英 泰法例可判死","createTime":"2017-06-14T12:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T11:26:48.000Z","uid":20170,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe48d36f9f46547e8e640d995b6f0a25eb8df46","tid":283813,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】東南亞國家普遍嚴打販毒，越南、馬來西亞、菲律賓、印尼、泰國等國的最高刑罰均為死刑，過往亦曾有港人涉毒而被判死及處決。而在今次案件中，由於可卡因在泰國屬「第二類毒品」，根據當地法例犯人不會被判死刑。<br />\n6年間5港人東南亞涉毒判死<br />\n根據泰國法例，海洛英、安非他命、冰毒、搖頭丸及黑芝麻迷幻藥為「第一類毒品」，任何人如持有或出售一定數量此類毒品，最高刑罰為死刑。而今次案件涉及的可卡因，屬於「第二類毒品」，任何人製造、入口或出口可卡因，最低刑罰為判囚二十年，最高刑罰可判終身監禁，罰款二百萬至五百萬泰銖（約四十六萬至一百一十四萬港元）。<br />\n國際特赦組織香港分會今年發表的報告指，在二○一二年至二○一七年間，該會曾接觸過五個港人於東南亞涉毒而被判死刑的個案。當事人通常聲稱不知情下販運毒品，在囚期間面對種族歧視、言語不通等問題，甚至請不到代表律師。其中香港女子林臻穎於二○一○年到馬來西亞探親，於檳城離境時替一名老婦拿袋，隨即被拘捕，袋中搜出一點八公斤海洛英，同年八月被判死刑，至今已過七年，家人仍為其奔走營救。<br />\n而另一香港男子黎兆祥則於二○一五年因涉毒而在印尼被判死，他聲稱被警方插贓及屈打成招，現正等候行刑。特首辦已分別致函馬來西亞駐港總領事和印尼駐港總領事，表示支持特赦林及黎的要求。<br />\n去年，四名港人梁樹福、盧榮輝、陳國棟及郭錦華，被控於菲律賓海域在漁船上製毒及藏毒，案件正審理中，如罪成勢面臨死刑。<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170607/mobile/odn-20170607-0607_00176_003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170607%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20170607-0607_00176_003.html&d=iSz0kT0cjQzK82TmM6ZXC54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e6704eff\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170607/mobile/odn-20170607-0607_00176_003.html</a><br />\n咁香港呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7505c9443faff2127f97c68b5070d996869c7c0e","tid":283813,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"東南亞國家普遍嚴打販毒<br />\n<br />\n其實點解既,背後有咩原因?"},{"pid":"345d04b0fe741c4a9b4e6d605b99f4c0ac034530","tid":283813,"uid":30788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東南亞國家普遍嚴打販毒<br />\n<br />\n其實點解既,背後有咩原因?</blockquote><br />\n因為毒品有毒"},{"pid":"195ece35f1b4a4b941166ddc00046531809ee533","tid":283813,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東</span></strong>"},{"pid":"86572990aefe8e4ce81e5ab358b9e8b4e3eaeab0","tid":283813,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17bd5f0b5a821c6d2bc4c26d086f37d5be11d065","tid":283813,"uid":59976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e07f53d74500088682db6423a5aaa83cbc4d9236","tid":283813,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:30:30.000Z","msg":"方向報真清楚"},{"pid":"23afa18b9a42e9cabc7cc008812cf3b2e6d413d8","tid":283813,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東南亞國家普遍嚴打販毒<br />\n<br />\n其實點解既,背後有咩原因?</blockquote><br />\n因為毒品有毒</blockquote><br />\n我係想知點解中東南國家嚴過其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c8887a0c3b8a49d7f0d247e2f93a4b7874bd65","tid":283813,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9656b1d117e2be2c6a259d405a10444f8b2e2151","tid":283813,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf03e2835a97cfa8f27c12cd5f62043f16baa116","tid":283813,"uid":83759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:40:05.000Z","msg":"於檳城離境時替一名老婦拿袋<br />\n當佢講真<br />\n有事無事都唔好幫唔識或唔熟識既人拎袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad281d84bc7f9552a8d5309991dc9081333003d","tid":283813,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>於檳城離境時替一名老婦拿袋<br />\n當佢講真<br />\n有事無事都唔好幫唔識或唔熟識既人拎袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個返大陸果陣呀媽次次都會講一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783f4d59e25798712670c9199c7869c226623198","tid":283813,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"入去坐比死更難受"},{"pid":"6544b02c101b9be62333543f39787a3b19fe8b9a","tid":283813,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>於檳城離境時替一名老婦拿袋<br />\n當佢講真<br />\n有事無事都唔好幫唔識或唔熟識既人拎袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依個真<br />\n我記得我小學個陣上常識個老師已經不停警告我地唔好亂幫人拎野，以前唔明點解，大過先知亂幫人拎野除時命都無"},{"pid":"17d7c835bbf2dde517893fd25ecdb8df27269aa0","tid":283813,"uid":81602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">方</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7a79c54f0d00bc59f64f161641681fc007f22d8d","tid":283813,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">方</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9286ac8202302886058d1cb20a6d6d591e8a25ba","tid":283813,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"146b590609dad988a60c33ab2b2690bc01b7b3f8","tid":283813,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68a1a8673e6d64af2f3cb6da008361ce0b390d0","tid":283813,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"909b2a99f3a85caf4ea3bd449dfd471