T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa140a65aef12796cbd23064e067d2609ddd0c3","tid":283813,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7997e23127c69a0d82fa28a7c365e2afdb229ef1","tid":283813,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3773cb9971ebbec383d4dace184558e3f3e9505","tid":283813,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:03:42.000Z","msg":"咁運白粉會點"},{"pid":"02357b78f61a7a26cc793263cb961dc973fe6880","tid":283813,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:05:55.000Z","msg":"於一九七四年，一個操控販毒集團多年的大毒梟吳錫豪（綽號「跛豪」）終於被警方毒品調查科拘捕，控以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">偷運毒品（主要來自泰國）</span></strong>來港。吳錫豪在一九七五年被法庭定罪及被判入獄30年。這是在當時的香港司法史上最長的判刑。吳的兩名副手則各被判入獄25年。&hellip;&hellip;於一九七七年，當局也下令通緝<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">馬惜如和馬惜珍兩兄弟（他們是吳錫豪以前的同黨）</span></strong>，打算控以在一九六八至七四年期間偷運700噸鴉片入口。"},{"pid":"b5958b2d1287071c73b6ad308019d81ba0809500","tid":283813,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"運鴉片呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c14eedfd86a21edc06915828e463e2f88d59193","tid":283813,"uid":5708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09e739c161c027b86b98c989dd45066ecf472d8c","tid":283813,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>運鴉片呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n Narcotics Categories in Thailand<br />\n<br />\nI &ndash; heroin, amphetamines (ecstasy), methamphetamines (Yaba and Ice)<br />\nII &ndash; morphine, cocaine, ketamine, codeine, opium and medicinal opium, methadone<br />\n<br />\nPossessing and Consuming Drugs in Thailand<br />\n<br />\nThailand&rsquo;s top 4 drug possession cases in the last three years have been related to the following drugs:  Yaba, dried marijuana, Ice, raw opium.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thailawforum.com/tourst-guide-laws-Thailand-4.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thailawforum.com%2Ftourst-guide-laws-Thailand-4.html&d=iSz0kT0cjQzK82TmM6ZXC54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=54533ae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thailawforum.com/tourst-guide-laws-Thailand-4.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFor Category 2 Substances:<br />\nUp to 10 years imprisonment and a fine of 100,000 &ndash; 1,000,000 Baht for production, importation or exportation. If the substance or substances found include morphine, opium or cocaine the penalty is increased to imprisonment of 20 years to life and fine of 2,000,000 &ndash; 5,000,000 Baht<br />\nUp to 10 years imprisonment and a fine of 20,000 &ndash; 200,000 Baht or both for disposal or possession for the purpose of disposal. In the case of morphine, opium or cocaine, 3-20 years or a fine of 60,000 &ndash; 400,000 Baht if the amount is under 100 grams, or 3-20 years or a fine of 500,000 &ndash; 5,000,000 Baht if over<br />\nUp to 5 years or a fine not exceeding 100,000 Baht or both for possession. If the quantity is 100 grams of a pure substance or more, this will be regarded as possession for the purpose of disposal<br />\nSix months to three years or a fine of 10,000 &ndash; 60,000 Baht or both for consumption<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.siam-legal.com/litigation/criminal-defence-drug-offences-in-thailand.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.siam-legal.com%2Flitigation%2Fcriminal-defence-drug-offences-in-thailand.php&d=iSz0kT0cjQzK82TmM6ZXC54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c1aef22c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.siam-legal.com/litigation/criminal-defence-drug-offences-in-thailand.php</a>"},{"pid":"4c3a369e71fcaca65aeaad0196493389d27770a9","tid":283813,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d93bb3b4b12819fb6d02d8db3076c3f5f8551407","tid":283813,"uid":68897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04d31367434813ef6367143a9e2ffaf168f42e28","tid":283813,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:15:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"639232ef25d81424018864bf922ab25f57f6ab50","tid":283813,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85074600f55bbda55cb74cdc096943d34b4edd24","tid":283813,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb080b86acee2bccd1eca261c630b925d25c9b52","tid":283813,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9207e514933806eb2b5da41b4c6864ce1348b578","tid":283813,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"328d240cc312d8f71a08e4ba4da1294a3c422026","tid":283813,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b4a52b7eb349aebaa0282f119a3a5912d34a36","tid":283813,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"去台灣就唔使判死la <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a0a65dd66d28c045d6e5589380b0f41d18fec5","tid":283813,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T